cheeks\u2019 electric pouches is stored inside its membrane and released while it is gliding."}, {"version": "black", "text": "The energy made in its cheeks\u2019 electric pouches is stored inside its membrane and released while it is gliding."}, {"version": "black-2", "text": "It glides on its outstretched membrane while shocking foes with the electricity stored in the pouches on its cheeks."}, {"version": "moon", "text": "It grills berries and bug Pok\u00e9mon with electric shocks and makes a meal of them. It usually nests in the holes gouged in trees by Pikipek."}, {"version": "omega-ruby", "text": "They live on treetops and glide using the inside of a cape-like membrane while discharging electricity."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "This Pok\u00e9mon absolutely loves sweet berries. Sometimes it stuffs its cheeks full of so much food that it can\u2019t fly properly."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "It glides using its cape-like membrane. Electrical energy scatters from it, shocking its friends and foes alike."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "As Emolga flutters through the air, it crackles with electricity. This Pok\u00e9mon is cute, but it can cause a lot of trouble."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "As it flies, it scatters electricity around, so bird Pok\u00e9mon keep their distance. That\u2019s why Emolga can keep all its food to itself."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "They store up electricity to fly through the air. When thunder cracks at night, sometimes there are almost enough of them to blot out the sky."}, {"version": "white", "text": "They live on treetops and glide using the inside of a cape-like membrane while discharging electricity."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "It glides on its outstretched membrane while shocking foes with the electricity stored in the pouches on its cheeks."}, {"version": "x", "text": "They live on treetops and glide using the inside of a cape-like membrane while discharging electricity."}, {"version": "y", "text": "